articles.author: Ryan Gaydos
articles.title: LSU defeats Clemson for college football national championship
articles.description: Who won the college football national championship?
articles.content:
LSU defeated Clemson, 42-25, to win the college football national championship Monday night.
It is LSU’s first national championship since the 2007 season.
